"{\"uid\": \"iheart.com-content-2024-08-12-colin-jost-shares-injury-update-after-paris-olympics-exit\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByJason Hall  August 12, 2024  Saturday Night Livewriter andWeekend Updateco-anchorColin Jostshared an injury update after days after his gig as a correspondent for the2024 Paris Olympicsended prior to the event's conclusion.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Dude, are you OK?'\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the no.\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 text message I have received in the past 48 hours.\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Usually followed by, 'Heard your foot fell off,' Well, I am actually fine!\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite what big media conspiracies would have you believe, I wasn't 'sent home' from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC simply looked at my food, declared me legally a leper, and exiled me here, to the island of Malta!\\\"\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9892472173468415, \"rank\": 0.00934150850621162, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.989602470920973, \"rank\": 0.01016171483786895, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jost joked in a video shared on his Instagram account.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.733564262108103e-15, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Colin Jost (@colinjost)  \\\"Now Malta does not have many Olympians competing this year, but it does have thousands of 15-year-old British kids competing to see who can black out the fastest, and somehow they are all winning,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colin Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\"}, {\"begin\": 701, \"end\": 706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.989602470920973, \"rank\": 0.01016171483786895, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}, {\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9976793690534028, \"rank\": 0.0019379984827675109, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also has this casino behind me, where I have blown the hundreds of dollars I have earned as a surfing correspondent.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the real reason I am in Malta of course is because it was the site of 10 separate bubonic plague outbreaks.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.989602470920973, \"rank\": 0.01016171483786895, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So they thought I would fit right in.\\\"\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC confirmed that Jost, 42, the husband of actressScarlett Johansson, who was in Tahiti covering surfing events \\\"stayed longer than originally planned\\\" due to weather issues in a statement toUSA TODAYlast Thursday (August 8).\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9892472173468415, \"rank\": 0.00934150850621162, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"score\": 0.9977522595065617, \"rank\": 0.001825941954815759, \"text\": \"Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\"}, {\"begin\": 1239, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Johansson\", \"score\": 0.9930381773771062, \"rank\": 0.006986208179988019, \"text\": \"Johansson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Johansson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Johansson\"}, {\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999946640927216, \"rank\": 5.335279264795927e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The competition ran long due to weather,\\\"NBCsaid.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He had a great time, and everyone was thrilled with his coverage from Tahiti.\\\"\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1529, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999946640927216, \"rank\": 5.335279264795927e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jost previously shared posts on his Instagram account of a foot injury he suffered on a coral reef during his Tahiti coverage, which soon became a staph infection.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.733564262108103e-15, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999946640927216, \"rank\": 5.335279264795927e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Colin Jost (@colinjost)  \\\"I have been visiting the medical tent regularly.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colin Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a weird feeling when you are in the medical tent way more than any of the athletes,\\\" Jost later toldNBC Sports.\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The medical staff at this point, they know my name, they are very familiar with my badge ID number, they know I am allergic to penicillin,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They started saying, 'We need to see you every day.'\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At first, I was like, 'Oh, my God, guys, I like you, too.'\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And they were like, 'No, it's because the infection has not improved.\\\"\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Colin Jost (@colinjost)  \\\"I vow, I will not leave here unless it's being evacuated in a helicopter,\\\" Jost joked.\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2267, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colin Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian weathermanLuke Bradnamtook over surfing coverage in Jost's absence,Reutersreported at the time.\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2381, \"end\": 2391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9615686720808829, \"rank\": 0.033314206290246125, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2444, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"score\": 0.9977522595065617, \"rank\": 0.001825941954815759, \"text\": \"Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \